description:
With @NoisiaRadio we hope to build a platform where we can play a wider range of music than we would in a club environment. It allows us to give some insights on the music we're feeling and releasing, as well as keeping our fans up to date more frequently and in a more accessible way than just by playing a show near you once a year or via the occasional video or message on social media.

Listen to more episodes and subscribe: www.noisia.nl/radio
NEW! Get a Noisia Radio T-Shirt: ​​​bit.ly/NoisiaRadioMerch

title: Noisia Radio

user.description: Noisia comprise Dutch producers Thijs, Nik and Martijn. Largely regarded as one of the most distinctive, powerful acts to emerge in bass music, their production techniques are referenced and praised across the entire electronic music scene. Their extensive body of work also includes the game Devil May Cry and the Foreign Beggars collaboration I Am Legion.
